[size=4][b]DaveDiverExpansion[/b][/size]

All-in-one diving enhancement mod for Dave the Diver.
Built on BepInEx 6 + HarmonyX. Open source on [url=https://github.com/WhiteMinds/dave-diver-expansion]GitHub[/url].

[size=3][b]Features[/b][/size]

[b]Auto Pickup[/b]
Automatically collects nearby fish, items, and treasure chests while diving.
[list]
[*]Configurable pickup radius
[*]Toggle fish / items / chests independently
[*]Smart filtering: skips weapons to prevent swap loops
[/list]

[b]Dive Map[/b]
Minimap HUD and full-level map overlay while diving.
[list]
[*]Minimap in the top-right corner, follows the player with configurable zoom
[*]Press [b]M[/b] to toggle a full-level enlarged map in the center of the screen
[*]Color-coded markers: escape pods (green), fish (blue), aggressive fish (red), items (yellow), chests (orange), O2 chests (cyan)
[/list]

[b]In-Game Config Panel[/b]
Press [b]F1[/b] to open a settings UI overlay.
[list]
[*]Auto-discovers all config entries from all features
[*]Toggle, slider, dropdown, and text input controls
[*]Changes take effect immediately
[/list]

[size=3][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Download [url=https://builds.bepinex.dev/projects/bepinex_be]BepInEx 6 Bleeding Edge[/url] — select [b]Unity.IL2CPP-win-x64[/b]
[*]Extract to your game folder: [font=Courier New]Steam\steamapps\common\Dave the Diver\[/font]
[*]Download the main file from the Files tab
[*]Extract the zip into the same game folder (it creates [font=Courier New]BepInEx\plugins\DaveDiverExpansion\[/font])
[*]Launch the game
[/list]

[size=3][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

Press [b]F1[/b] in-game to open the built-in settings panel. All settings can be adjusted live and are saved automatically.

You can also edit the config file directly:
[font=Courier New]Dave the Diver\BepInEx\config\com.davediver.expansion.cfg[/font]

[size=3][b]Settings[/b][/size]

[b]AutoPickup[/b]
[list]
[*][font=Courier New]Enabled[/font] (default: true) — Master toggle
[*][font=Courier New]AutoPickupFish[/font] (default: false) — Auto-collect dead fish
[*][font=Courier New]AutoPickupItems[/font] (default: true) — Auto-collect dropped items
[*][font=Courier New]AutoOpenChests[/font] (default: false) — Auto-open treasure chests
[*][font=Courier New]PickupRadius[/font] (default: 1.0) — Collection radius in game units
[/list]

[b]DiveMap[/b]
[list]
[*][font=Courier New]Enabled[/font] (default: true) — Enable the dive map HUD
[*][font=Courier New]ToggleKey[/font] (default: M) — Key to toggle the enlarged map
[*][font=Courier New]ShowEscapePods[/font] (default: true) — Show escape pod markers
[*][font=Courier New]ShowFish[/font] (default: false) — Show fish markers
[*][font=Courier New]ShowItems[/font] (default: false) — Show item markers
[*][font=Courier New]ShowChests[/font] (default: false) — Show chest markers
[*][font=Courier New]MapSize[/font] (default: 0.3) — Minimap size (fraction of screen height)
[*][font=Courier New]MapOpacity[/font] (default: 0.8) — Map opacity
[*][font=Courier New]MiniMapZoom[/font] (default: 3.0) — Minimap zoom level
[/list]

